Class ReportObjectOutputStreamImpl

Direct Known Subclasses:
ReportObjectOutputFileStream
public abstract class ReportObjectOutputStreamImpl
extends DataObjectOutputStreamImpl
implements ReportObjectOutputStream

The abstract base class for SIF_ReportObject OutputStreams to which ReportPublishers write the results of a query.

This class extends DataObjectOutputStreamImpl to handle packetizing logic that is specific to SIF_Responses that contain SIF_ReportObject payloads.
